{"section": "4.8.6: Examples of counting subsets.", "qid": 1, "input_type": "input", "instructions": "<div class=\"activity-instructions\">\n <p>\n  For the following questions, express your answer as\n  <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n   \"n choose r\"\n  </span>\n  . Ex:\n  <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n   8 choose 3\n  </span>\n  .\n </p>\n</div>\n", "question": "<div>\n <div class=\"text\">\n  A file will be replicated on 3 different computers in a distributed network of 15 computers. How many ways are there to select the locations for the file?\n </div>\n</div>", "correct_choice_index": null, "choices": [], "answer": "15 choose 3\nor\n15 choose 12", "explanation": "<div aria-atomic=\"true\" class=\"explanation has-explanation forfeit\" role=\"alert\">\n <p class=\"message\">\n  Answers\n </p>\n <div class=\"answers\">\n  <!-- -->\n  <span class=\"forfeit-answer\">\n   15 choose 3\n  </span>\n  <span class=\"or-text\">\n   or\n  </span>\n  <span class=\"forfeit-answer\">\n   15 choose 12\n  </span>\n </div>\n In determining the locations for the file, a 3-subset is selected from the set of 15 computers, so the number of choices is\n <span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n </span>\n <span class=\"MathJax_SVG\" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"&gt;&lt;mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\"&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\"&gt;&lt;mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-OPEN\"&gt;&lt;mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\"&gt;(&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;mfrac linethickness=\"0\"&gt;&lt;mn&gt;15&lt;/mn&gt;&lt;mn&gt;3&lt;/mn&gt;&lt;/mfrac&gt;&lt;mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\"&gt;&lt;mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-CLOSE\"&gt;&lt;mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\"&gt;)&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' id=\"MathJax-Element-22-Frame\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 100%; display: inline-block; position: relative;\" tabindex=\"0\">\n  <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"3.384ex\" role=\"img\" style=\"vertical-align: -1.005ex;\" viewbox=\"0 -1024.6 1624.8 1457.1\" width=\"3.774ex\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\">\n   <g fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\">\n    <use x=\"0\" xlink:href=\"#MJSZ1-28\" y=\"-1\">\n    </use>\n    <g transform=\"translate(458,0)\">\n     <g transform=\"translate(0,443)\">\n      <use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-31\">\n      </use>\n      <use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" x=\"500\" xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-35\" y=\"0\">\n      </use>\n     </g>\n     <use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" x=\"250\" xlink:href=\"#MJMAIN-33\" y=\"-488\">\n     </use>\n    </g>\n    <use x=\"1166\" xlink:href=\"#MJSZ1-29\" y=\"-1\">\n    </use>\n   </g>\n  </svg>\n  <span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\">\n   <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n     <mrow>\n      <mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\">\n       <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-OPEN\">\n        <mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\">\n         (\n        </mo>\n       </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n      <mfrac linethickness=\"0\">\n       <mn>\n        15\n       </mn>\n       <mn>\n        3\n       </mn>\n      </mfrac>\n      <mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\">\n       <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-CLOSE\">\n        <mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\">\n         )\n        </mo>\n       </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n     </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n   </math>\n  </span>\n </span>\n <script id=\"MathJax-Element-22\" type=\"math/tex\">\n  {15 \\choose 3}\n </script>\n</div>\n"}